The Peoples’ Democratic Party (PDP) appears to be coasting to victory in Abuja Municipal Area Council (AMAC) at the just concluded FCT Council elections. At the resumption of votes collation at the Local Government centre Sunday morning, the PDP lead in 10 out of 11 Council Wards collated. The breakdown of the votes for AMAC chairmanship as returned from each ward are as follows: WARD – NYANYA
